## Critical Success Metrics

1. **Tenant Isolation:** Data from one tenant never visible to another
2. **AI Agent Response Time:** < 3 seconds for Q&A, < 10 seconds for task creation
3. **Automation Coverage:** 80% of routine tasks automated with HITL gates
4. **Update Propagation:** New features deployable to all tenants within 1 hour
5. **Customization Overhead:** < 5% code duplication for tenant-specific features

---

## Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|------------|
| RLS performance issues | Index all `org_id` columns, use IMMUTABLE functions |
| AI agent hallucinations | Constrained tool use, human verification gates |
| Tenant data leaks | Comprehensive RLS testing, automated security scans |
| Update breaking clients | Feature flags, staged rollouts, rollback capability |
| Scope creep | Strict 5-day deadline, MVP-first approach |

